cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS, cs.SE 

This paper discusses the issue of concept drift in machine learning, which is a common problem in many real-world applications of machine learning. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and software engineering (cs.SE).
